com.github.bordertech.wcomponents

Class WMenuItemGroup

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.github.bordertech.wcomponents.AbstractWComponent
      • com.github.bordertech.wcomponents.AbstractContainer
        • com.github.bordertech.wcomponents.WMenuItemGroup
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Container, Disableable, WComponent, WebComponent, Serializable

    public class WMenuItemGroup
extends AbstractContainer
implements Disableable
    This component provides a logical grouping of related menu items. The rendered version in the UI usually provides a visual grouping as well, including the menu item group's title.
    Since:
    1.0.0
    Author:
    Yiannis Paschalidis
